Install APM Server on Windows

For installing the APM Server we need to do the following:

1) Download the APM Server from the download page of Elastic (https://www.elastic.co/downloads/apm).
2) Extract the downloaded zip content under C:\Program Files.
3) Rename the long directory name with the version name appended to it, to a clean name like "apm-server"
    With Administration rights, open the PowerShell and run following command:

	cd 'C:\Program Files\apm-server'
	.\install-service-apm-server.ps1

This will install APM Server on Windows machine.
